column5: Here a few pictures of some fish that we caught last weekend.  Enjoy!  Jeff
Nice pics! Looks like a great weekend
way to go !   beautiful color on the fish.  jason
Nice eyes looks like you had a great weekend  rob
Nice fish....amazing pics...what kind of Camera are you using?

I have two cameras depending on the day and if I even bring either of them.  I have a Canon Digital SLR and a Point and Shoot.  I love the SLR, although all of these were taken with the Point and Shoot as the conditions weren't going to be great so I didn't bring the SLR out.  Perhaps this weekend I will.  Jeff
Nice catch !!!!...great looking quinte walleyes for sure .  ...cheers
Very nice catch with beautiful pictures to boot  Got myself a Canon as well and can't wait to snap a couple of fish so people actually beleive I catch fish, lol!  Thanks for the report  reefrunner
